{"title":"Linux文件传输服务-klsday6","uid":"32ad3e8d6b6ba6d99339baf1198a4c1f","slug":"klsday6-Linux","date":"2023-05-22T01:01:23.423Z","updated":"2023-05-23T04:57:16.422Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/klsday6-Linux.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/wallhaven-7p382e_2.png","content":"<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522090704625.png\" alt=\"image-20230522090704625\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"Samba-文件共享服务\"><a href=\"#Samba-文件共享服务\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Samba 文件共享服务\"></a>Samba 文件共享服务</h2><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522090810486.png\" alt=\"image-20230522090810486\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"Samba服务基础\"><a href=\"#Samba服务基础\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Samba服务基础\"></a>Samba服务基础</h3><p>Samba是一种开源软件，它的功能是在Linux&#x2F;UNIX操作系统上实现与Windows操作系统的互操作性。主要用途是实现文件和打印机共享。</p>\n<p>使用Samba服务可以将Linux&#x2F;UNIX操作系统上的文件共享给Windows客户端，并且可以让Windows客户端通过网络打印机协议打印到Linux&#x2F;UNIX系统上面的打印机，实现跨平台文件和打印机共享。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522090934092.png\" alt=\"image-20230522090934092\"></p>\n<p>Windows和Linux的Samba服务是互通的</p>\n<p>Windows的创建快捷方式可以直接创建访问共享文件夹的快捷方式</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522212800750.png\" alt=\"image-20230522212800750\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522213232693.png\" alt=\"image-20230522213232693\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522091444645.png\" alt=\"image-20230522091444645\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522215143306.png\" alt=\"image-20230522215143306\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"主配置文件-x2F-etc-x2F-samba-x2F-smb-conf\"><a href=\"#主配置文件-x2F-etc-x2F-samba-x2F-smb-conf\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"主配置文件&#x2F;etc&#x2F;samba&#x2F;smb.conf\"></a>主配置文件&#x2F;etc&#x2F;samba&#x2F;smb.conf</h3><p>主配置文件默认分成了四个部分<code>global，homes，printers，自定义名字</code></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522092535941.png\" alt=\"image-20230522092535941\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522094041582.png\" alt=\"image-20230522094041582\"></p>\n<p>所属工作组基本不用了</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522220227999.png\" alt=\"image-20230522220227999\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">Samba服务包括哪2个主程序?各自的作用是什么?\nsmbd：smbd是Samba服务器的核心守护进程。它负责处理来自Windows客户端的文件和打印请求，并与客户端共享 Linux 文件系统上的文件和打印机。\nnmbd：nmbd是Samba服务器中的名称解析器守护进程。它负责将NetBIOS名称解析为IP地址并向网络广播Samba服务器的存在，以便Windows客户端能够查找和连接到Samba服务器。\n\nSamba服务使用到了哪些协议、端口?\nTCP端口139：用于SMB协议的NetBIOS会话服务。\nTCP端口445：用于SMB协议的直接主机间通信（Direct Host-to-Host Communication）服务。\nUDP端口137：用于NetBIOS名字服务（NetBIOS Name Service）。\nUDP端口138：用于NetBIOS数据报服务（NetBIOS Datagram Service）。</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"构建文件共享服务器\"><a href=\"#构建文件共享服务器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"构建文件共享服务器\"></a>构建文件共享服务器</h3><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522100645186.png\" alt=\"image-20230522100645186\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522101238987.png\" alt=\"image-20230522101238987\"></p>\n<p><code>pdbedit -a -u abyssaler</code>的作用是为名为 <code>abyssaler</code> 的用户添加一个新的 Samba 账户，随后会让你创建密码，<code>-a</code> 表示添加新用户，<code>-u abyssaler</code> 指定要添加用户的用户名为 <code>abyssaler</code></p>\n<p>启动服务</p>\n<p>centos：<code>systemctl restart smb nmb</code></p>\n<p>Ubuntu：<code>systemctl restart smbd nmbd</code></p>\n<p>尝试用Windows主机来访问</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522221321023.png\" alt=\"image-20230522221321023\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522221340021.png\" alt=\"image-20230522221340021\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522221346675.png\" alt=\"image-20230522221346675\"></p>\n<p>这就是samba1的家目录</p>\n<p>Windows删除samba登陆记录：命令行输入<code>net use * /del</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"设置用户授权访问\"><a href=\"#设置用户授权访问\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"设置用户授权访问\"></a>设置用户授权访问</h3><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522101534862.png\" alt=\"image-20230522101534862\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">vaild users-----设定只有此名单内的用户才能访问共享资源(拒绝优先)(用户名&#x2F;@组名) \ninvalid users---设定只有此名单内的用户不能访问共享资源(拒绝优先)(用户名&#x2F;@组名)\nread list-------设定此名单内的成员为只读(用户名&#x2F;@组名) \nwrite list------若设定为只读时，则只有此设定的名单内的成员才可作写入动作(用户名&#x2F;@组名)\nvalid group-----指定访问共享所需的用户组。该选项的值是一个组名，默认为空。\n\n除了可以使用用户权限相关的选项，还有一些其他的常用选项\npath------------指定共享的本地路径，Samba 将会在此路径下创建一个名为 &lt;共享名称&gt; 的共享目录。\npublic----------规定是否允许未授权的用户访问共享。如果设置为 Yes，则所有用户都可以访问该共享，否则只有经过验证的用户才能够访问。默认值为 No。\ncomment---------为共享提供一个简短的描述（注释），以便于辨识和说明。\nbrowseable------指定此共享是否在 Windows 网络浏览器中显示,默认值为 Yes。\nguest ok--------规定是否允许匿名访问,默认值为 No。\n\n涉及多个用户用逗号隔开</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522104920390.png\" alt=\"image-20230522104920390\"></p>\n<p><code>directory mask</code>：该选项用于指定在创建新目录时应该设置的默认UNIX权限掩码。</p>\n<p><code>create mask</code>：该选项用于指定在创建新文件时应该设置的默认UNIX权限掩码。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">小练习：\n创建共享目录：share和manager\n创建访问用户 admin，zhangsan，jingli1，jingli2\n创建访问组：managers\n权限需求1：share可以被所有人访问下载，但是只有admin可以上传\n权限需求2：manager目录只有属于manager组的用户和admin可以访问下载，其他人无权限访问，而admin除了下载还有上传权限。</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">解答：\n先建共享目录\nmkdir -p &#x2F;data&#x2F;SamShare\ncd &#x2F;data&#x2F;SamShare\nmkdir share\nmkdir manager\n\n建立用户\nsudo useradd sambaAdmin\nsudo useradd sambaJingli1\nsudo useradd sambaJingli2\nsudo useradd sambaZhangsan\n添加samba用户\nsudo pdbedit -a -u sambaAdmin\nsudo pdbedit -a -u sambaJingli1\nsudo pdbedit -a -u sambaJingli2\n默认用户名和密码相同\n\n建立访问组\nsudo groupadd -g 1500 sambaManagers\nsudo gpasswd -M sambaJingli1,sambaJingli2 sambaManagers\n\n配置samba权限\n编辑samba配置文件&#x2F;etc&#x2F;samba&#x2F;smb.conf\nvim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;samba&#x2F;smb.conf\n\n配置如下：\n[share]\ncomment &#x3D; shared directory\npath &#x3D; &#x2F;data&#x2F;SamShare&#x2F;share\npublic &#x3D; yes\nread only &#x3D; yes\nwrite list &#x3D; sambaAdmin\n\n[manager]\ncomment &#x3D; manager directory\npath &#x3D; &#x2F;data&#x2F;SamShare&#x2F;manager\nvalid users &#x3D; @sambaManager, sambaAdmin\npublic &#x3D; no\nread only &#x3D; yes\nwrite list &#x3D; sambaAdmin</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522112605730.png\" alt=\"image-20230522112605730\"></p>\n<p>小练习权限设置参考：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522104830646.png\" alt=\"image-20230522104830646\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522180917268.png\" alt=\"image-20230522180917268\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">Unix_name：samba账号的名称\nSMB_name1：要修改的别名\n别名最好是系统中不存在的</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">创建smbusers文件\nvim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;samba&#x2F;smbusers\nsamba1 &#x3D; bieming1 bieming2\n然后在主配置文件的global中声明别名文件的所在位置\nusername map &#x3D; &#x2F;etc&#x2F;samba&#x2F;smbusers\n然后重启服务即可\nsystemctl restart smb nmb</code></pre>\n\n<p>然后在Windows用同样的方法访问</p>\n<p>id：bieming1</p>\n<p>passwd：samba1</p>\n<p>同样可以访问samba1的共享文件夹</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522105721212.png\" alt=\"image-20230522105721212\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">smbclient -L 192.168.4.11 # 查看指定远程主机有哪些共享\nsmbclient -U zhangsan -L 192.167.4.11  # 指定用户\n\n加!再执行命令相当于在本地执行命令</code></pre>\n\n<p>在Ubuntu防火墙中确保相应的samba端口打开</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">启用防火墙（如已启用可忽略）\nsudo ufw enable\n检查 Samba 端口是否已在防火墙规则中开放\nsudo ufw app list\n查找 &quot;Samba&quot; 应用\nubuntu@VM-12-6-ubuntu:&#x2F;data&#x2F;SamShare$ sudo ufw app list\nAvailable applications:\n  Apache\n  Apache Full\n  Apache Secure\n  OpenSSH\n  Samba\n如果未找到 &quot;Samba&quot; 应用程序，则可以使用以下命令手动添加规则：sudo ufw allow Samba\n但是这里有，所以就不添加了\n输入以下命令，以允许Samba协议通过139和445端口：\nsudo ufw allow 139&#x2F;tcp\nsudo ufw allow 445&#x2F;tcp\n重新加载防火墙规则：\nsudo ufw reload\n重新启动Samba服务：\nsudo systemctl restart smbd.service\n\n防火墙关闭samba的端口\n输入以下命令以停止 Samba 服务\nsudo systemctl stop smbd.service\n输入以下命令以禁用 Samba 服务的自动启动\nsudo systemctl disable smbd.service\n使用以下命令将 139 和 445 端口添加到已拒绝访问的端口列表\nsudo ufw deny 139&#x2F;tcp\nsudo ufw deny 445&#x2F;tcp\n重新加载防火墙规则\nsudo ufw reload</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522110715374.png\" alt=\"image-20230522110715374\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522111022839.png\" alt=\"image-20230522111022839\"></p>\n<p><strong>注意：samba只能用于局域网</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522111306848.png\" alt=\"image-20230522111306848\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522183238169.png\" alt=\"image-20230522183238169\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522183248352.png\" alt=\"image-20230522183248352\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522111529743.png\" alt=\"image-20230522111529743\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"FTP\"><a href=\"#FTP\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"FTP\"></a>FTP</h2><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522133010070.png\" alt=\"image-20230522133010070\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"ftp概述\"><a href=\"#ftp概述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ftp概述\"></a>ftp概述</h3><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522133226671.png\" alt=\"image-20230522133226671\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522133934549.png\" alt=\"image-20230522133934549\"></p>\n<p>匿名用户，本地用户数据直接用明文传输，抓包一抓一个准</p>\n<h3 id=\"ftp配置\"><a href=\"#ftp配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ftp配置\"></a>ftp配置</h3><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522134244700.png\" alt=\"image-20230522134244700\"></p>\n<p><code>/etc/vsftpd/ftpusers</code>控制黑名单</p>\n<p><code>/etc/vsftpd/user_list</code>只是一个用户列表，它要配合ftp主配置文件中的如下两个选项来使用</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230523104709989.png\" alt=\"image-20230523104709989\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"全局配置\"><a href=\"#全局配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"全局配置\"></a>全局配置</h4><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522134627972.png\" alt=\"image-20230522134627972\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"匿名配置\"><a href=\"#匿名配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"匿名配置\"></a>匿名配置</h4><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522135503358.png\" alt=\"image-20230522135503358\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"本地用户配置\"><a href=\"#本地用户配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"本地用户配置\"></a>本地用户配置</h4><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522135811204.png\" alt=\"image-20230522135811204\"></p>\n<p>本地用户不用指定<code>local_root=</code>根目录，因为本地用户登陆以后，都是在你的家目录（<code>chroot_local_user</code>将你禁锢到家目录），在本地用户在家目录所有权限都是满的</p>\n<h3 id=\"ftp应用\"><a href=\"#ftp应用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ftp应用\"></a>ftp应用</h3><h4 id=\"匿名访问实验\"><a href=\"#匿名访问实验\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"匿名访问实验\"></a>匿名访问实验</h4><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522135942486.png\" alt=\"image-20230522135942486\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230523123800481.png\" alt=\"image-20230523123800481\"></p>\n<p>还要添加一句<code>anon_other_write_enable=YES</code></p>\n<p>验证：在Windows目录栏输入<code>ftp://192.168.2.237</code></p>\n<p> <img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230523124515223.png\" alt=\"image-20230523124515223\"></p>\n<p>这个目录就是ftp服务器的<code>/var/ftp/pub</code>目录</p>\n<p>赋予pub文件夹权限：<code>chmod 777 /var/ftp/pub</code></p>\n<p>然后就可以上传文件，创建目录，删除文件了</p>\n<h4 id=\"本地登陆实验\"><a href=\"#本地登陆实验\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"本地登陆实验\"></a>本地登陆实验</h4><p>想登录ftp，系统账户必须要有密码</p>\n<p>在匿名登陆页面右击</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230523125443013.png\" alt=\"image-20230523125443013\"></p>\n<p>输入系统账号密码即可登陆</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522153740194.png\" alt=\"image-20230522153740194\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522153902014.png\" alt=\"image-20230522153902014\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522154154098.png\" alt=\"image-20230522154154098\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522154252684.png\" alt=\"image-20230522154252684\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522154504723.png\" alt=\"image-20230522154504723\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522154614279.png\" alt=\"image-20230522154614279\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522154947354.png\" alt=\"image-20230522154947354\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230522155340165.png\" alt=\"image-20230522155340165\"></p>\n","feature":true,"text":" Samba 文件共享服务 Samba服务基础Samba是一种开源软件，它的功能是在Linux&#x2F;UNIX操作系统上实现与Windows操作系统的互操作性。主要用途是实现文件和打印机共享。 使用Samba服务可以将Linux&#x2F;UNIX操作系统上的文件共享给Win...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.5k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"学习笔记","slug":"学习笔记","count":20,"path":"api/categories/学习笔记.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"kls","slug":"kls","count":8,"path":"api/tags/kls.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Samba-%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Samba 文件共享服务</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Samba%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Samba服务基础</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%BB%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6-x2F-etc-x2F-samba-x2F-smb-conf\"><span class=\"toc-text\">主配置文件&#x2F;etc&#x2F;samba&#x2F;smb.conf</span></a></li><li class=\"to